府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=ad4f1fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"676e8ea9b52dd0ab2ee8772e11f906fb619d408a","tid":2032372,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"簽幾多都係冇用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a6ae4f80423ba4611a32d9baf145f800ccfff5","tid":2032372,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"識玩梗係去簽名支持,<br />\n再同D職員熱烈地交流啦...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過講得性起喉嚨乾咳幾聲呢D好正常"},{"pid":"011a1d0cce17d447daa5932ae6b83a5912842b28","tid":2032372,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79657eb77f2559b41d57d5be9f6c7d48dc7b55ac","tid":2032372,"uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"中環3個鐘都無人簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"星期日咁多菲傭鬼理你<